msgstr "Automatisk registrering"

#: uconf.rs_badge_flash_help
msgid "This controls how Trndi's icon in the status bar and/or tray will notify you visually."
msgstr "Dette styrer, hvordan Trndis ikon i statuslinjen og/eller bakken giver dig visuel besked."

#: uconf.rs_beta
msgid ""
"This backend is in a beta stage, it may not work as intended!\n"
" If possible, choose another backend."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_beta_dex
msgid ""
"This is a new Deccom backend, it's in a beta stage! If possible, choose the old backend.\n"
"Please set your own thresholds in the Customization tab."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_choose_system
msgid "Select your CGM system in the list, then enter your credentials"
msgstr "Vælg dit CGM-system på listen, og angiv derefter dine oplysninger"

#: uconf.rs_clear_margin_help
msgid "Once an alert triggers, the reading must recover this many units past the threshold before the alert can fire again."
msgstr "Når en alarm udløses, skal aflæsningen komme dette mange enheder forbi grænsen, før alarmen kan udløses igen."

#: uconf.rs_color_bg
msgid "Trndi can draw a rectangle/background in the graph's background, to visually represent your high and low limits."
msgstr "Trndi kan tegne en rektangel/baggrund i grafens baggrund for visuelt at repræsentere dine høje og lave grænser."

#: uconf.rs_connect_help
msgid "This will display a badge showing the internet connectivity status in the top."
msgstr "Dette viser et badge øverst, der viser internettilslutningsstatus."

#: uconf.rs_current_acc
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "This only applies for the current loaded account:  %s"
msgstr "Dette gælder kun for den aktuelle indlæste konto: %s"

#: uconf.rs_current_acc_def
msgid "Settings for \"default\" only apply while multi-user is active"
msgstr "Indstillinger for \"standard\" gælder kun, mens flerbruger er aktiv"

#: uconf.rs_current_acc_no
msgid "These settings are available when using a multi-account"
msgstr "Disse indstillinger er tilgængelige ved brug af flere konti"

#: uconf.rs_custom_range_help
msgid "Override/set your own limits for the custom range. This is your personal ideal goal, within the high/low area."
msgstr "Tilsidesæt/sæt dine egne grænser for det tilpassede område. Dette er dit personlige ideelle mål inden for høj/lav-området."

#: uconf.rs_debug_backend_label
msgid "(Ignored for debug backend)"
msgstr "(Ignoreret i fejlfindingstilstand)"

#: uconf.rs_debug_warn
msgid ""
"This is a debug backend. It's used for testing purposes only!\n"
"No data will be sent to any remote server."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_decimal_help
msgid "This replaces the decimal separator, eg setting \",\" will show the reading as 5,5 instead of 5.5"
msgstr "Dette erstatter decimaltegnet, f.eks. indstilling af \",\" viser aflæsningen som 5,5 i stedet for 5.5"

#: uconf.rs_default_account
msgctxt "uconf.rs_default_account"
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Standard"

#: uconf.rs_delta_max
msgid "When the previous reading is missing, use the next available reading within this many 5-minute-intervals to calculate delta."
msgstr "Når den forrige aflæsning mangler, bruges den næste tilgængelige aflæsning inden for dette antal 5-minutters-intervaller til at beregne delta."

#: uconf.rs_dex
msgid ""
"Dexcom servers do not provide custom high and low blood sugar values.\n"
"Please set your own thresholds in the Customization tab."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_diff_right_help
msgid "This controls if the difference/delta will show center or right (when predictions are on, this will swap the position of the values)"
msgstr "Dette styrer, om forskel/delta vises i center eller til højre (når forudsigelser er slået til, vil dette bytte om på positionerne)"

#: uconf.rs_disable_media
msgid "This turns off all media-related features. Can speed up start."
msgstr "Dette slår alle medierelaterede funktioner fra. Kan fremskynde opstart."

#: uconf.rs_display_advanced_help
msgid "When supported by the backend, the sensor expiration time can be shown in Trndi"
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_display_general_help
msgid ""
"- A progressbar can show the time until the next update on the left hand side of the screen\n"
"- The time can we displayed every 20 seconds, instead of the Reading\n"
"- The reading and trend arrow can alternate positions"
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_display_window_help
msgid ""
"- The background color can be set to the current glucose range color\n"
"- The window can stay over other windows\n"
"- The window's borders can be hidden (may depend on operating system)"
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_driver_contributor
msgid "Driver contributor: "
msgstr "Bidragyder: "

#: uconf.rs_dupe_name
msgid "Names must be unique"
msgstr "Navne skal være unikke"

#: uconf.rs_empty_proxy
msgid "Proxy host is empty."
msgstr "Proxyserveren er tom."

#: uconf.rs_enter_any
msgid "Please enter a name"
msgstr "Angiv venligst et navn"

#: uconf.rs_enter_name
msgid "Letters, space and numbers only"
msgstr "Kun bogstaver, mellemrum og tal"

#: uconf.rs_enter_user
msgid "Enter a username"
msgstr "Angiv et brugernavn"

#: uconf.rs_err_address
msgctxt "uconf.rs_err_address"
msgid "Address must start with http(s)://"
msgstr "Adressen skal starte med http(s)://"

#: uconf.rs_err_email
msgctxt "uconf.rs_err_email"
msgid "You must enter a valid e-mail address"
msgstr "Du skal angive en gyldig e-mailadresse"

#: uconf.rs_err_password
msgctxt "uconf.rs_err_password"
msgid "You must enter a password"
msgstr "Du skal angive en adgangskode"

#: uconf.rs_extcount
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "Extensions count: %d"
msgstr "Antal udvidelser: %d"

#: uconf.rs_ext_reload_done
msgid "Extensions were reloaded."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_ext_reload_title
msgid "Reload Extensions"
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_ext_requests
msgid "Requests: "
msgstr "Anmodninger: "

#: uconf.rs_font_help
msgid "You can change the font of the reading, time and arrow. Click on the respective item here to change the font"
msgstr "Du kan ændre skrifttypen for aflæsning, tid og pil. Klik på det respektive element her for at ændre skrifttypen"

#: uconf.rs_full_arrow_set_help
msgid "This will display all prediction arrows, by default Trndi just shows going up, down or steady"
msgstr "Dette viser alle forudsigelsespile; som standard viser Trndi blot op, ned eller stabilt"

#: uconf.rs_hastouch
msgid "Shows if Trndi detected a touch screen"
msgstr "Viser om Trndi registrerede en touchskærm"

#: uconf.rs_min_minutes
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "When calculating time-in-range, do so over this amount of minutes. If the number is higher than the data available, the max time will be used - this is currently %d minutes."
msgstr "Ved beregning af tid i målområdet bruges dette antal minutter. Hvis tallet er højere end tilgængelige data, bruges maxtiden - dette er i øjeblikket %d minutter."

#: uconf.rs_multi_user_help
msgid ""
"Trndi supports <b>more than one user</b>, this is called the <i>multi user mode</i>.<br>In this section you can add/remove accounts. There's <i>always</i> a default account which cannot be deleted.\n"
"Accounts have their own settings and remote servers, and are <i>\"sandboxed\"</i>.<br><br>Start a new instance of Trndi to log in to a given user account."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_must_persist_help
msgid "An alert will only trigger if the condition has been true continuously for this many minutes. Set to 0 to trigger immediately."
msgstr "En alarm udløses kun, hvis betingelsen har været opfyldt kontinuerligt i dette antal minutter. Sæt til 0 for at udløse med det samme."

#: uconf.rs_newver
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "Version %s is available, would you like to go to the downloads page? You can also ignore this warning for 2 weeks."
msgstr "Version %s er tilgængelig, vil du gå til downloadsiden? Du kan også ignorere denne advarsel i 2 uger."

#: uconf.rs_newver_caption
msgid "New version available"
msgstr "Ny version tilgængelig"

#: uconf.rs_newver_pre
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "A new pre-release for %s is available, would you like to go to the downloads page?"
msgstr "En ny forhåndsversion af %s er tilgængelig, vil du gå til downloadsiden?"

#: uconf.rs_notifications
msgctxt "uconf.rs_notifications"
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "Notifikationer"

#: uconf.rs_notification_help
msgid "Trndi will show a system notification (if available) when your reading is in a dangerous state. Alerts will trigger once when hi/low and every 15 minutes when readings are missing."
msgstr "Trndi viser en systemnotifikation (hvis tilgængelig) når din aflæsning er i en farlig tilstand. Advarsler udløses én gang ved høj/lav og hvert 15. minut, når aflæsninger mangler."

#: uconf.rs_notify_system
msgid "Notifications will appear where you normally get notification messages."
msgstr "Notifikationer vises, hvor du normalt modtager notifikationsbeskeder."

#: uconf.rs_notify_title
msgid "A notification system is required"
msgstr "Et notifikationssystem er påkrævet"

#: uconf.rs_notify_txt
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "Trndi uses a system called \"%s\" to send desktop notices, you need to have this system installed in order to receive notices."
msgstr "Trndi bruger et system kaldet \"%s\" til at sende skrivebordsnotifikationer; du skal have dette system installeret for at modtage notifikationer."

#: uconf.rs_no_copyright
msgid "- Extension has no copyright info -"
msgstr "- Udvidelsen har ingen copyrightinfo -"

#: uconf.rs_no_extensions
msgid "This version of Trndi does not support extensions"
msgstr "Denne version af Trndi understøtter ikke udvidelser"

#: uconf.rs_no_extensions_copyright
msgid "Please download a version of Trndi that supports extensions"
msgstr "Download venligst en version af Trndi, der understøtter udvidelser"

#: uconf.rs_no_extensions_system
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "Due to hardware limitations, %s on %s cannot support extensions"
msgstr "På grund af hardwarebegrænsninger kan %s på %s ikke understøtte udvidelser"

#: uconf.rs_outdated_help
msgid "This is the time after which Trndi will show the \"no recent\" readings overlay. Trndi checks this when updating from the remote server, not every minute."
msgstr "Dette er den tid, hvorefter Trndi viser overlay'et \"ingen nylige\" aflæsninger. Trndi kontrollerer dette ved opdatering fra fjernserveren, ikke hvert minut."

#: uconf.rs_override_help
msgid ""
"Setting values here allows you to define your own high and low blood sugar limits in Trndi.\n"
"\n"
"NightScout:\n"
"Trndi automatically retrieves your custom high and low settings from NightScout, so manually setting them here is usually unnecessary.\n"
"\n"
"Dexcom:\n"
"Dexcom servers do not provide custom high and low values. By setting them here, you can establish your own thresholds for Dexcom data."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_override_language
msgid "Choose which language to run Trndi in. Should you choose the wrong one, you can press the Windows/\"meta\" button at start to force English!"
msgstr "Vælg hvilket sprog Trndi skal køre på. Hvis du vælger forkert, kan du holde Windows/\"meta\"-knappen nede ved start for at tvinge engelsk!"

#: uconf.rs_override_ns
msgid "You are using the NightScout backend, you should set these values on your server (if possible), as Trndi uses your NightScout preferences by default"
msgstr "Du bruger NightScout-backend, du bør indstille disse værdier på din server (hvis muligt), da Trndi bruger dine NightScout-præferencer som standard"

#: uconf.rs_pos
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "This feature depends on your Window Manager (WM). %s may not support this feature."
msgstr "Denne funktion afhænger af din vinduesmanager (WM). %s understøtter muligvis ikke denne funktion."

#: uconf.rs_pos_title
msgid "Restricted Feature"
msgstr "Begrænset funktion"

#: uconf.rs_pos_unknown
msgid "This feature depends on your Window Manager. It may not support this feature."
msgstr "Denne funktion afhænger af din vinduesmanager (WM). Den understøtter muligvis ikke denne funktion."

#: uconf.rs_predictionwarn
msgid "Trndi will try to predict future readings. This is experimental and potentially unsafe! Do not make any treatment decisions based on these values! This feature is used on your own risk and responsibility!"
msgstr "Trndi vil forsøge at forudsige fremtidige aflæsninger. Dette er eksperimentelt og potentielt usikkert! Træf ingen behandlingsbeslutninger baseret på disse værdier! Du bruger funktionen på egen risiko og ansvar!"

#: uconf.rs_prediction_help
msgid "Trndi can predict/guess what your reading will be in the future. This will be shown in the lower right part of the screen."
msgstr "Trndi kan forudsige/gætte hvad din aflæsning vil blive i fremtiden. Dette vises i skærmens nedre højre hjørne."

#: uconf.rs_prediction_horizon
msgid "The prediction horizon is how far in the future Trndi will show predictions, when just showing one. This is not an exact time, it may vary, it's just a target time."
msgstr "Forudsigelseshorisonten er, hvor langt ind i fremtiden Trndi forudsiger aflæsninger, når kun én vises. Tiden er ikke eksakt, den kan variere, det er kun en måltid."

#: uconf.rs_pred_scale_help
msgid "When predictions are enabled, this controls the size adjustment of the predictions"
msgstr "Når forudsigelser er aktiveret, styrer dette størrelsesjusteringen af forudsigelserne"

#: uconf.rs_privacy_help
msgid "When in Privacy Mode, the actual blood glucose value is hidden. Trndi will only tell the user if it's good, high or low."
msgstr "I privatlivstilstand er den faktiske blodglukoseværdi skjult. Trndi viser kun om værdien er god, høj eller lav."

#: uconf.rs_remove_acc
msgid "Removed accounts are made inactive, and can be restored by adding the same name again"
msgstr "Fjernede konti gøres inaktive og kan gendannes ved at tilføje samme navn igen"

#: uconf.rs_rotating_arrow_help
msgid "Instead of the fixed up/steady/down arrows, the trend arrow is rotated smoothly to match how fast your glucose is changing: nearly flat for small changes and leaning further down (or up) the faster it moves."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_saftey_hi
msgid "Trndi won't allow a larger limit, for your own safety. This can be overridden manually/via plugin"
msgstr "Trndi tillader ikke en større grænse, for din egen sikkerhed. Dette kan tilsidesættes manuelt/via plugin"

#: uconf.rs_saftey_low
msgid "Trndi won't allow a lower limit, the backend system only reports values every 5 minutes. 6 = one reading missing."
msgstr "Trndi tillader ikke en lavere grænse, backendsystemet rapporterer kun værdier hvert 5. minut. 6 = én aflæsning mangler."

#: uconf.rs_scale_diff_help
msgid "You can change the scale/size of the difference in reading since last, by entering a scale factor"
msgstr "Du kan ændre skalaen/størrelsen for forskellen siden sidst ved at angive en skalafaktor"

#: uconf.rs_select_font
msgid "Select a font"
msgstr "Vælg en skrifttype"

#: uconf.rs_select_font_arrow
msgid "Select a font for the arrow"
msgstr "Vælg en skrifttype til pilen"

#: uconf.rs_select_font_desc
msgid "Choose a font to use"
msgstr "Vælg en skrifttype"

#: uconf.rs_select_font_reading
msgid "Select a font for the reading"
msgstr "Vælg en skrifttype til aflæsningen"

#: uconf.rs_select_font_time
msgid "Select a font for the time"
msgstr "Vælg en skrifttype til tiden"

#: uconf.rs_shortmode_full
msgid "By default, Trndi only shows up/down/straight. You can enable the full range of arrows here - however you must realize that this is very experimental and potentially less accurate!"
msgstr "Som standard viser Trndi kun op/ned/lige. Du kan aktivere det fulde sæt af pile her - men du skal være klar over, at dette er meget eksperimentelt og potentielt mindre nøjagtigt!"

#: uconf.rs_short_mode_help
msgid "Only one reading will show, as just an arrow or a single prediction"
msgstr "Kun én aflæsning vises, i form af en pil eller en enkelt forudsigelse"

#: uconf.rs_tandem
msgid ""
"This backend is in alpha stage, it may not work as intended!\n"
"Please set your own thresholds in the Customization tab."
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_test_fail
msgid "Could not connect!"
msgstr "Kunne ikke oprette forbindelse!"

#: uconf.rs_test_success
msgid "Successfully connected!"
msgstr "Forbundet!"

#: uconf.rs_test_unsupported
msgid "Sorry! Trndi does not (yet) support connection testing for this service!"
msgstr "Beklager! Trndi understøtter (endnu) ikke forbindelsestest for denne tjeneste!"

#: uconf.rs_threashold_lines_help
msgid "Trndi can draw a line on the graph's background, to represent where your high/low limits are."
msgstr "Trndi kan tegne en linje på grafens baggrund for at repræsentere dine høje/lave grænser."

#: uconf.rs_timestamp_help
msgid "By default Trndi shows the amount of minutes since the last reading, this setting allows you to display the time of the last reading instead."
msgstr "Som standard viser Trndi antallet af minutter siden seneste aflæsning; denne indstilling giver mulighed for i stedet at vise tidspunktet for aflæsningen."

#: uconf.rs_update_snooze
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "You will be alerted again after %s"
msgstr "Du vil blive advaret igen efter %s"

#: uconf.rs_uptodate
msgid "You are up to date"
msgstr "Du er opdateret"

#: uconf.rs_uptodate_dev
#, object-pascal-format
msgid "You are using a development version, there's no stable release newer than this! The most recent stable release is %s"
msgstr "Du bruger en udviklingsversion, der er ingen stabil udgivelse nyere end denne! Den seneste stabile udgivelse er %s"

#: uconf.rs_use_url_help
msgid "Trndi can load a URL when high or low in your default web browser."
msgstr "Trndi kan indlæse en URL i din standardwebbrowser, når du er høj eller lav."

#: uconf.rs_warn_hilow
msgid "This will show an overlay on the screen when a low or high is predicted"
msgstr "Dette viser et overlay på skærmen, når et lavt eller højt niveau forudsiges"

#: uconf.rs_wayland
msgid ""
"Your desktop session is Wayland. Wayland compositors (including KWin) restrict third-party apps from forcing windows above others.\n"
"Right-click the title bar, select more options and check the always-on-top option (or similar)"
msgstr ""

#: uconf.rs_webapi
msgid "Trndi can expose a <b>WebAPI</b> for use with <i>third-party systems</i>.<br><br>This is an advanced feature, you can safely disregard it if you don't know what it does!"
msgstr "Trndi kan starte et <b>Web-API</b> til brug med <i>tredjepartssystemer</i>.<br><br>Dette er en avanceret funktion; du kan roligt se bort fra den, hvis du ikke ved, hvad den gør!"

#: uconf.rs_xdrip
msgid ""
"Make sure you are on the same network as the xDrip app.\n"
"Make sure that web access is turned on."
msgstr ""

#: ufloat.rs_custom_op
msgctxt "ufloat.rs_custom_op"
msgid "You can use shift+<number> to manually set visibility (0 = 100% visible)"
msgstr "Du kan bruge skift+<nummer> til manuelt at angive synlighed (0 = 100% synlig)"

#: ufloat.rs_custom_size
msgctxt "ufloat.rs_custom_size"
msgid "You can hold down shift and plus (+) or minus (-) to change the window size"
msgstr "Du kan holde skift og plus (+) eller minus (-) nede for at justere vinduesstørrelsen"

